NEO Magazine - Issue 139 2015
=============================
English | 100 pages | True PDF | 24 MB


Head into the darkness of the universe as we hitch a ride with the craziness that is Space Dandy - back for a second season of madness! Also, see our gallery of winners from the NEO Art Competition held at the MCM Comic Con in May, read our interview with Hidetaka Tenjin - mecha genius - and find out more about Bandai Namco's incoming Godzilla game! All that plus the latest anime from Rumiko Takahashi, the latest releases from your favourite manga, anime and Asian movie distributors, plus news, reviews, cosplay and more!
